title: 200PCS Disposable Plastic Microblading Honeycomb Tattoo Ink Cups
desc: Description:/nExperience a versatile set up with the innovatively designed Hive Caps./nThese tattoo ink cap pieces can be used individually or can be snapped together and configured in countless ways, allowing for convenient arrangement and organization of your palette as needed./nHive Caps can also be stacked to prevent ink from drying out and to reduce the risk of contamination, making them ideal for use at conventions or during longer tattoo sessions.
